.row
  .col-md-12
    %h2
      %i.fa.fa-phone-square
        #{page.title}

    %p
      Once you have activated your scanner and joined the Resistance you should 
      %em
        "ask to join"
      any local communities below and reach out to your nearby fellow Resistance agents via faction comms. They can help you with portal locations, supplies, tactics, levelling up and the best places for food and drinks when the Ingressing gets too much (or you're waiting for a portal to cool down).
.row
