    %h4 Victoria Wide

    %p
      After you 
      %em
        "ask to join"
      this community go to
      %a{:href=>"http://ingress.com/intel"} ingress.com/intel
      and centre your map over Melbourne then in faction chat broadcast your Google+ initials to prove your Resistance credentials e.g.
      %em
        "request to join g+ group, my initials are JB @nicktorious @maiestia @puddle @simonoid"
      or if you already know a Resistance member ask them to vouch for you in the group and a mod will invite you.

    %p
      The 
      %em
        @nicktorious @maiestia @puddle @simonoid
      part makes it easier for our mods to see your request and add you to the community quicker.

    %p
      %i.fa.fa-lock
      This community is for verified Resistance members only.

    %p
